Sentencas: Crofer 22 and Haynes 230 alloys, which are candidates for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) interconnects, were exposed at 800 degrees C to a simulated coal syngas (29.1CO + 28.5H(2) + 11.8CO(2) +
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas
Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas

Sentencas: The samples were characterized by SEW/EDS, XRD and ASR.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas

Sentencas: Results indicated that the compositions of the oxide scales in syngas and in air were similar.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas

Sentencas: For Crofer 22, scales formed in both air and coal syngas were composed of (Cr,Fe)(2)O-3, Mn-Cr compounds and Fe3O4.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas

Sentencas: For Haynes 230 the main composition was Cr2O3.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas

Sentencas: However, it was found that the morphologies of the scales formed in coal syngas were different from those formed in air.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas

Sentencas: Besides, the cross section element distributions of oxide scales formed on Crofer 22 were disparate.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas

Sentencas: In addition, the ASR values of the oxide scales formed in coal syngas and in air were similar at 800 degrees C but the activation energies for electronic conduction of the oxide scales formed in coal syngas were higher.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnects for SOFC in coal syngas
